{"tid":1125964,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新貓入屋問題","createTime":"2019-04-26T05:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T10:09:51.000Z","uid":169559,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ff67a5a9598d8d30fc275c5eb1d8d2a2208385b7","tid":1125964,"uid":169559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"我領養左隻家貓 大約7個月大<br />\n黎左我屋企已經個幾月 但佢都係好驚人 <br />\n我係房行出廳佢一定會跑走 搵地方匿<br />\n你靠近佢佢會飛機耳/對耳縮去後面 然後saaaa咁發惡<br />\n係咪同佢由細到大都係流浪貓有關呢 佢真係好細膽<br />\n我之前想摸佢都俾佢抓左好多次 抓到我唔敢再摸佢<br />\n<br />\n請問各位巴打有咩方法可以令佢適應得易啲同無咁驚人？"},{"pid":"c7afe0bd98f30ab6e0be6e97b6f60f1fdfccf841","tid":1125964,"uid":169559,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:13:28.000Z","msg":"附上貓圖一張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eo6pe7p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEo6pe7p.png&h=10421899&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dd2969836dc9f58af7f2a9c2f73077e50e880a6","tid":1125964,"uid":249562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e34c710a5a9d97dafd6c26587ef81fb486be5ed7","tid":1125964,"uid":169559,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrkmhnf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyrkmhnf.png&h=34279dbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c209c59d5061c9622df5f18a42de07a8288d7108","tid":1125964,"uid":1408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:08:22.000Z","msg":"你俾啲舊衫佢索下你陣味先啦"},{"pid":"2150d515bb99b4adaafcc6cc67d5d3b93cff16ab","tid":1125964,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:09:09.000Z","msg":"試下用feliway"},{"pid":"36c4ee2dec2f4e0e7abfb6a091f2970d477b5116","tid":1125964,"uid":59920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:13:44.000Z","msg":"Free慣仲要俾你困籠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"