以試吓俾巴哈花精貓貓食呀，之前用過好似真係穩定到貓貓情緒。<br />\n如果佢宜家咁驚，直接滴落口應該有難度，可以滴落佢個水碗到等佢飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係iherb有得買<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ryUY734.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FryUY734.png&h=257c4b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd237759f8695a3359ae610b142d8af6f0542ca4","tid":1125964,"uid":48500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:25:39.000Z","msg":"玩下貓棒比下零食,可能流浪多驚人,由佢周圍走熟下環境熟左就會好d"},{"pid":"143eff23a144c195d4f641eb73f3a5f846be1229","tid":1125964,"uid":41714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:52:19.000Z","msg":"圖唔夠. 好難分析呀"},{"pid":"b272f3cfa6f61bc77fe1badb4079fe6c7fb489ea","tid":1125964,"uid":8701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7SDoOe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7SDoOe.png&h=4fccbc09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P896xGA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP896xGA.png&h=a157ad02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我2隻領養返黎2個月，仲係一行近就Feaaaaaa😭<br />\n希望你果隻唔會🥺"},{"pid":"531a50ea57836e0b1bcf22c80b2ccbae62702744","tid":1125964,"uid":41714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b272f3cfa6f61bc77fe1badb4079fe6c7fb489ea","tid":1125964,"uid":8701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7SDoOe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7SDoOe.png&h=4fccbc09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P896xGA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP896xGA.png&h=a157ad02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我2隻領養返黎2個月，仲係一行近就Feaaaaaa😭<br />\n希望你果隻唔會🥺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:02:11.000Z","msg":"佢有佢ffiend, 你有你驚👍🏻"},{"pid":"fcf81b46644a9326435ba2eba461fadb96844f7a","tid":112596